    "Evaluation": {
      "text": "CT neck with IV contrast\nGold standard",
      "subsections": {
        "XR_Soft_tissue": {
          "text": "Neck in extension at end inspiration\nThe prevertebral space should be less than 7mm at C2, 14mm at C6 in children regardless of the age\nThe prevertebral space should be less than 22mm at C6 in adults\nThe prevertebral space should be less than one-half the width of the corresponding vertebral body\nIf equivocal XR, order CT",
          "tables": []
