      "text": "Emergent ENT consult\nMost patients require\nI&D\nIndications for drainage - trismus, rim enhancement on CT\nSecure airway - care must be taken to minimize contact with\nabscess\nas rupture is significant risk\nTracheostomy\nor fiberoptic\nintubation\nmay be necessary\nCT or MRI may help prepare for method of definitive airway\n[2]",
